<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xsl:stylesheet version="1.1"
	xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xmlns:fo="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format"
	exclude-result-prefixes="fo" xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/02/xpath-functions"
	xmlns:java="java">

	<xsl:template match="/" name="LPL-EXCEPTION-VT">
		
		<fo:block margin-top="0.2in" margin-left="0.2in" margin-right="0.2in">
					<fo:block font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-weight="bold" text-align="center"
						font-size="12px">UNITED STATES FIRE INSURANCE COMPANY
					</fo:block>
					<fo:block font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-weight="bold" text-align="center"
						font-size="12px" space-after="4mm">THE NORTH RIVER INSURANCE COMPANY
					</fo:block>
					<fo:block font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-weight="bold" text-align="center"
						font-size="12px" space-after="6mm">LAWYERS PROFESSIONAL LIABILITY MANUAL
					</fo:block>
					<fo:block font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" text-align="center"
						font-size="11px" space-after="6mm">VERMONT EXCEPTION PAGE
					</fo:block>
					
					<fo:block font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" text-align="center"
						font-size="11px" space-after="6mm">SECTION I – GENERAL RULES
					</fo:block>
					
					<fo:block space-after="8mm">	
					<fo:list-block>

					<fo:list-item space-after="4mm">
						<fo:list-item-label>
							<fo:block font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-size="10px">
								<fo:inline>2.	</fo:inline>
							</fo:block>
						</fo:list-item-label>
						<fo:list-item-body>
							<fo:block start-indent="14mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-size="10px">
									<fo:block space-after="4mm">
										POLICY FORM
									</fo:block>
									<fo:block space-after="4mm" text-align="justify">
										United States Fire Insurance Company/The North River Insurance Company
										(the “Insurer”) has a duty to defend the policyholder and such defense
										expenses are paid on behalf of the policyholder. All coverage provided
										by the policy is in excess of the deductible, which applies to each
										claim, unless the policy is endorsed otherwise. The policy is
										non-cancellable except for nonpayment of premium or deductible and is
										written on a claims-made-and-reported basis.
									</fo:block>
									
						</fo:block>
					</fo:list-item-body>
				</fo:list-item>
				<fo:list-item space-after="4mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-size="10px">
						<fo:list-item-label>
							<fo:block>
								<fo:inline>5.	</fo:inline>
							</fo:block>
						</fo:list-item-label>
						<fo:list-item-body>
							<fo:block start-indent="14mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-size="10px">
									<fo:block space-after="4mm">
										LIMITS OF LIABILITY
									</fo:block>
									<fo:block space-after="4mm" text-align="justify">
										Optional limits of liability are available with this policy. The
										minimum limit is $100,000 each claim/$300,000 in the policy aggregate,
										inclusive of defense expenses; the maximum limit available is
										$5,000,000 each claim/$5,000,000 in the policy aggregate. Defense
										expenses are in addition to the damages limit.
									</fo:block>
									
						</fo:block>
					</fo:list-item-body>
				</fo:list-item>
				</fo:list-block>
				</fo:block>
					<fo:block font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" text-align="center"
						font-size="11px" space-after="4mm">SECTION II – RATING METHODOLOGY
					</fo:block>
					
					<fo:block font-weight="bold" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-size="11px" space-after="4mm" text-align="justify">
					STEP 1.
					</fo:block>
					
					<fo:block font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-size="11px" space-after="4mm" text-align="justify">
					The absolute base rate is $3,454.00 per lawyer applicant.
					</fo:block>
					
					<fo:block font-weight="bold" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-size="11px" space-after="4mm" text-align="justify">
					STEP 4.
					</fo:block>
					
					<fo:block font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;" font-size="11px" space-after="4mm" text-align="justify">
						Determine the modification factor for Limit of Liability and Deductible
						choice by using the appropriate page of Chart E (Select chart 2 or 5
						depending upon whether the deductible will apply to each claim, or be
						an annual aggregate.) Then, from Chart F apply the modifier for the
						option of “first dollar defense coverage” i.e. the deductible on the
						policy applies to damages only and not to defense expenses. Then, from
						Chart G apply the modifier for the option of “career coverage” i.e.
						coverage for professional services performed by a lawyer prior to
						joining the firm.
					</fo:block>
					
					<fo:block space-after="4mm">
						<fo:table>
						 <fo:table-column column-width ="65mm" />
						 <fo:table-column column-width="100mm"/>
						 <fo:table-body>
					    		  <fo:table-row>
					                    <fo:table-cell padding-left="0.5cm">
					                    <fo:block text-align="left" font-size="10px" space-after="4mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">
					                    	a – CHART E (1 of 2) –
					                    </fo:block>
					                    </fo:table-cell>
					                    <fo:table-cell>
					                    <fo:block text-decoration="underline" text-align="left" font-size="10px" space-after="4mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">
					                    	Increased Limit Factor/Deductible Factor
					                    </fo:block>
					                    </fo:table-cell>
					              </fo:table-row>
					               <fo:table-row>
					                    <fo:table-cell padding-left="0.5cm" padding-top="3mm">
					                    <fo:block text-align="left" font-size="10px" space-after="4mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">
					                    	b – CHART F –
					                    </fo:block>
					                    </fo:table-cell>
					                    <fo:table-cell padding-top="3mm">
					                    <fo:block text-decoration="underline" text-align="left" font-size="10px" space-after="4mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">
					                    	First Dollar Defense Option
					                    </fo:block>
					                    </fo:table-cell>
					              </fo:table-row>
					              <fo:table-row>
					                    <fo:table-cell padding-left="0.5cm" padding-top="3mm">
					                    <fo:block  text-align="left" font-size="10px" space-after="4mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">
					                    	c – CHART G –
					                    </fo:block>
					                    </fo:table-cell>
					                    <fo:table-cell padding-top="3mm">
					                    <fo:block text-decoration="underline" text-align="left" font-size="10px" space-after="4mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">
					                    	Career Coverage Modification
					                    </fo:block>
					                    </fo:table-cell>
					              </fo:table-row>
						</fo:table-body>
						</fo:table>
					</fo:block>
					<fo:block  text-align="justify" font-size="10px" space-after="4mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">
						The three factors above are multiplied (a X b X c) to determine the Step 4 modification factor.
					</fo:block>
					
					<fo:block  text-align="justify" font-size="10px" space-after="4mm" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">
						Charts E-1, E-3, E-4 and E-6 are deleted.
					</fo:block>
					
					<fo:block margin-top="5cm" />
					<fo:block font-size="9px" color="grey" text-align="left" font-family="Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;">
						LPL-VT (04/17)&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;
						&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;
						&#160;&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160; &#160;
						&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;
						&#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160; &#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160; &#160;
						&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160; &#160;
						&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160; &#160;
						&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Page 1 of 1
					</fo:block>
</fo:block>

	</xsl:template>
</xsl:stylesheet>
